+# Neural ICE: NVIDIA open GPU out-of-tree modules, signed by the base kernel's
+# ephemeral module-signing key. Only built for the base (up) variant we ship.
+%if %{with_up_base}
+%package modules-nvidia-open
+Summary: NVIDIA open GPU (r595) kernel modules for kernel %{KVERREL}
+Requires: %{name}-modules-core-uname-r = %{KVERREL}
+Provides: %{name}-modules-nvidia-open-uname-r = %{KVERREL}
+Provides: installonlypkg(kernel-module)
+%description modules-nvidia-open
+The NVIDIA open GPU (r595) out-of-tree kernel modules, built against and signed
+by the ephemeral per-build module-signing key of this exact %{KVERREL} kernel.
+The private half of that key is discarded at the end of the build, so these
+modules load only in this kernel and the key cannot be re-used to sign anything
+else.
+%endif
