+# Neural ICE: NVIDIA open GPU modules (signed by the ephemeral module key).
+# No depmod scriptlet: this subpackage installs in the SAME transaction as the
+# kernel, whose %posttrans runs `depmod -a <kver>` over the whole module tree
+# (incl. extra/nvidia-open). The atomic bootc image never updates it on its own,
+# so a per-subpackage depmod would be redundant.
+%if %{with_up_base}
+%files modules-nvidia-open
+%defattr(-,root,root)
+%dir /lib/modules/%{KVERREL}/extra/nvidia-open
